   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Payout Schedules are generated for every period for the programâ€™s lifespan. For example, if the Billing Frequency is <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Monthly</b> and the program is setup for two years, there will be 24 Billing Schedules generated when the program is activated.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Billing Schedules have their own life cycle and are affected by the program life cycle.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <fig class="- topic/fig ">
            <image height="198"
                   placement="break"
                   width="700"
                   href="../attachments/102432692/102432747.png"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Payout Schedule Status</b>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col3" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Status</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Transition</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Description</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Pending</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">When Schedule is activated</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Future Period</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Open</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Date driven from Pending</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Current period: start date &lt; today &lt; end date + grace period Calculations are ongoing</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Ready</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Date driven from Open</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Period is available for a downstream gathering of results: today &gt; end date + grace period</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Closed</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Event driven from Ready</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Downstream processes have locked the period for audit/reference purposes.</p>
                        <p class="- topic/p ">All related Aggregated Results are closed</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Aggregated and detail calculation results are associated with <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Open</b> and <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Ready</b> schedules. Schedules with a Ready status indicate that calculation is no longer occurring, and results are <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Ready</b> to be sent to or picked up by downstream applications. After the calculated result is consumed, statuses are updated to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Closed.</b> For Billing program results, when the invoice is approved, statuses are updated.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Calculation Result Status</b>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col3" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Status</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Transition</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Description</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Open</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Container schedule becomes Active</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Aggregated Results are calculated based on calculation frequency while the Schedule is Open.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Ready</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Container schedule becomes Ready</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Aggregated Results are not calculated automatically anymore. Container schedule is Ready.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Closed</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Event driven</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Downstream application has updated Aggregated Results as immutable. For example, the related Invoice has been processed, or Payment created.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
